lines: 1. Mobake Omonda Yeso,Mo'ekengw'anso bonoEr'otwabeir'ebibeOmogwenia oito;Momobake, momobake,Omogambi botambe.
3. Buna Tat'ogotorendaEre otomanyire,Atotaboria riokaKorw'ase ababisa;Momobake, momobake,Abar'ang'e na aare.
4. Amalaika mobake,Inwe morochaine,Erioba n'omotienyiBikomotung'amera;Momobake, momobake,Yes'Omond'O igoro.
